{"tid":1626233,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【身體很誠實】《我和我的祖國》4日票房僅收77萬 香港藍絲都唔睇","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T08:51:20.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ec1318daf6382b30c9a4d8464a0f7bdbbfe6b747","tid":1626233,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:16:44.000Z","msg":"中共建政70年，大陸連續有幾日假期，10.1檔期票房相當出色，愛國電影《我和我的祖國》、《中國機長》及《攀登者》截至今日合共取得38億人民幣票房。單是陳凱歌擔任總導演的《我》片上映6日約收17.5億人民幣，同日開畫的《中》片和《攀》片就分別收約14.5億及6.5億，但與香港票房比較成強烈對比，香港觀眾似乎對獻禮片毫不賣賬。<br />\n英皇公司負責安排《我》片在港發行上映，10.1首天開畫有41萬票房，影片上映了4天也不過是77萬，李仁港執導的《攀》片就4日約收38萬，從票房反映普遍香港觀眾對這類愛國電影並不熱衷支持。至於劉偉強執導的《中》片就因香港近期局勢問題，還未安排映期。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191005/large/1570265151_95a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191005%2Flarge%2F1570265151_95a7.jpg&h=901a09ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191005/60120836\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191005%2F60120836&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=9ddf7327\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191005%2F60120836&h=610e370e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191005/60120836</a>"},{"pid":"e27a04b0504de7eb836805aabf50b1ab6102286d","tid":1626233,"uid":181778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94b712c883ceef6761050b7b1276d53837c746d6","tid":1626233,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:19:30.000Z","msg":"捉鳩班支那狗睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日睇五次篤數"},{"pid":"26b71aded43873b44e63a5fe009532d7